# Cursor Style Test
# Tests bar cursor style with custom color
Output examples/svgs/cursor-style-test.svg

Set Width 500
Set Height 200
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme gruvbox-dark
Set Title "Bar Cursor Style"

# Use bar cursor style with green color
Set CursorStyle bar
Set CursorColor #50fa7b

Type "echo 'This uses a bar cursor'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "echo 'with a custom green color'"
Enter
Type "COOL"
Shift+Left 4
Sleep 200ms
Backspace
Enter
Sleep 1s
